mating the aggregate properties as an\nexpectation over the joint distribution outperforms point estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jan 2020 02:43:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 00:50:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-28"}
