lations, we develop a hydrodynamics code\nthat makes use of standard finite-volume methods coupled with a multigrid\nmetric solver to solve the Einstein equations in the CFC approximation. In this\npaper, we present the methodology and implementation of our code Gmunu and its\nproperties and performance in some benchmarking relativistic hydrodynamics\nproblems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jan 2020 10:07:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 11:39:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 08:30:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-24"}
