powers associated\nwith all three basic scattering mechanisms are estimated with a non-negligible\nerror higher than 10% for some cases. Despite these conclusions are subject to\na particular model and inversion approach they suggest that a careful\nconsideration of physically-based decompositions outcomes should be taken.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jan 2020 15:09:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-17"}
